    Product	Are your products genetically modified?	No, all of our products are non-GMO!
    Product	What is the best way to store your products?	Always store your oil in a cool, dry place, sheltered from light and heat.
    Company	Where can I find the best buy date?	Our best buy dates are printed on the back of our bottles in the American format (month/day/year)
    Product	Are your products kosher?	Yes, our products are kosher!
    Product	Are your products dairy free?	Yes, our products are dairy free!
    Order	Do you offer wholesale?	For any wholesale inquiries, please visit www.orlandofoods.com
    Shipping	Do you ship internationally?	At this time we only ship within the USA.
    Shipping	Do you have physical coupons available?	No, at this time we do not have coupons available to mail. 
    Company	Where can I find Olitalia next?	Head to our Events page to see where we'll be! 
    Order	Can I cancel my subscription?	Yes, you can cancel  your subscription at any time. 
    Shipping	Can I get my order on the same day?	No, we are unable to deliver your products same day.
    Order	Can I cancel my order?	Unfortunately, once orders are placed, they cannot be cancelled.
    Order	Can I exchange/return my order?	For any information regarding returns and exchanges, please contact us at ___. Any concerns regarding orders not placed on usa.olitalia.com or from a retailer must be communicated directly to that vendor. Unfortunately, we cannot assist with returns or replacements for products purchased outside of usa.olitalia.com
